data.description: Beautiful Bungalow in a fantastic Medlock location.? This perfect 2 bed 1 bath home sits on a true nature lovers lot that is also large and level. Thoughtfully renovated with an open kitchen, solid stone countertops, eat in area, classic white cabinets, and hardwoods.? Great natural light throughout the home, large bedrooms, sun room, & renovated bath.? Excellent entertaining areas including a side yard deck & fenced back yard with an awesome fire pit. Storage building and yes even a babbling creek as well.? Quiet, peaceful, and all with easy access to Medlock Park, South Peachtree Creek Trail, and the Clyde Shepherd Nature Preserve. Close to shopping and restaurants, CDC and Emory.
